definitions.definition: The daughter of Helios and the sister of Circe . She was raised as a princess at Cholchis , and then given in marriage to King Minos of Crete . With Minos, she was the mother of Ariadne , Androgeus , Glaucus , Deucalion , Phaedra , and Catreus . She was also the mother of the Minotaur .
One of the moons of Jupiter .
